{"segment":2,"line_start":46,"line_end":100,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"你懂不懂这是什么意思。","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":56,"line_end":56},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"我懂。","tone":"平静","chapter":3,"line_start":58,"line_end":58},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"你能不能告诉我？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"能。","tone":"平静","chapter":3,"line_start":62,"line_end":62},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"石米的意思，是不是用石头做成的米？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":64,"line_end":64},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"不是，石头不是米，石头不能做米，石头不能吃，石头如果能吃，世上就没有饿死的人了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":66,"line_end":67},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":null,"text":"那是藏语。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":70,"line_end":70},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"在藏语，石米是什么。","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":72,"line_end":72},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"是猫。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"猫？","tone":"惊讶","chapter":3,"line_start":76,"line_end":76},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"猫！","tone":"认真","chapter":3,"line_start":78,"line_end":78},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"猫有什么可怕？连鱼都不怕猫，鱼怕的是人，抓鱼的人。","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":90,"line_end":91},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"对。","tone":"平静","chapter":3,"line_start":94,"line_end":94},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"只有老鼠才怕猫。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":96,"line_end":96},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"char_xiao_fang","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"错。","tone":"认真","chapter":3,"line_start":98,"line_end":98}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[],"locations":[],"items":[]},"entity_updates":[]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":101,"line_end":146,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"你说的是不是圣母之水峰？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"在峰上的妖魔就是猫，虽然它身子已炼成人形，它的头还是猫。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":112,"line_end":113},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"柯拉柯罗是什么？","tone":"疑问","chapter":3,"line_start":116,"line_end":116},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"是强盗，一种最凶恶的强盗，不但要劫人的钱，还要吃人的血肉。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":118,"line_end":119},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"他们大部分都是藏边深山中的'果尔洛人'，他们的生活和语言都与别人不同，而且凶悍野蛮，比哈萨克人更残酷。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":122,"line_end":123},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"果尔洛在梵文中还另外有种意思。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":126,"line_end":126},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":"char_bu_ying","text":"什么意思？","tone":"好奇","chapter":3,"line_start":128,"line_end":128},{"speaker":"char_bu_ying","speaker_name":"卜鹰","listener":"char_xiao_fang","text":"怪头。","tone":"陈述","chapter":3,"line_start":130,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":null,"text":"猫头人身的妖魔，残酷野蛮的怪头强盗。","tone":"无奈","chapter":3,"line_start":132,"line_end":132},{"speaker":"char_xiao_fang","speaker_name":"小方","listener":null,"text":"难怪这个人怕得这么厉害，现在我都有点怕了。","tone":"无奈","chapter":3,"line_start":134,"line_end":134}],"new_entities":{"characters":[],"skills":[],"techniques":[],"factions":[{"id":"faction_guo_er_luo_ren","name":"果尔洛人","type":"帮派","location":"藏边深山","sub_divisions":[],"one_line":"藏边深山中凶悍野蛮的族群，梵文意为'怪头'，被称作猫盗","source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":122,"line_end":123,"text":"他们大部分都是藏边深山中的'果尔洛人'，他们的生活和语言都与别人不同，而且凶悍野蛮，比哈萨克人更残酷。"},{"chapter":3,"line_start":126,"line_end":126,"text":"果尔洛在梵文中还另外有种意思。"}]}],"locations":[{"id":"loc_sheng_mu_zhi_shui_feng","name":"圣母之水峰","region":"大地边缘","one_line":"大地边缘比天还高的山峰，万古不化冰雪，传说有猫首人身的妖魔","source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":106,"line_end":108,"text":"故老相传，在大地的边缘，有一处比天还高的山峰，山上不但有万古不化的冰雪，而且还有种比恶鬼更可怕的妖魔。"},{"chapter":3,"line_start":110,"line_end":110,"text":"你说的是不是圣母之水峰？"}]}],"items":[{"id":"item_mao_shou_ren_shen_qi","name":"猫首人身旗","type":"special","owner":"char_su_ma","one_line":"苏玛手中绣有猫首人身妖魔图案的小旗，猫盗标志","description":"一面小旗，上面绣着猫首人身的妖魔图案，是猫盗（柯拉柯罗）的标志旗帜，令藏人苏玛见之五体投地、膜拜不止。","effects":[],"origin":"猫盗","rarity":"寻常凡品","related_characters":["char_su_ma"],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[],"source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":138,"line_end":138,"text":"他手里紧紧握着一面小旗，上面绣着的赫然正是一个猫首人身的妖魔。"}]}]},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_xiao_fang","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":16,"line_end":18,"text":"一转过沙丘，他就立刻看到了一幕他这一生永远都忘不了的景象。如果不是他的胃已经空了，他很可能会呕吐。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_bu_ying","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"初识，小方向卜鹰请教猫盗之事"}]},{"id":"char_bu_ying","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":48,"line_end":50,"text":"卜鹰的脸上连一点表情都没有。卜鹰身上每根血管流着的好像都不是血，是冰水。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_xiao_fang","type":"合作者","intensity":40,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"初识，卜鹰向小方解释猫盗传说"}]},{"id":"char_wei_tian_peng","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":22,"line_end":22,"text":"卫天鹏的旋风三十六把快刀，已倒下了三十四个。"},{"chapter":3,"line_start":136,"line_end":136,"text":"卫天鹏忽然拉起苏玛一只不停在抽筋的手，把他的手指一根根扳开。"}]},"relationship_updates":[]},{"id":"char_su_ma","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":3,"line_start":34,"line_end":34,"text":"苏玛今年五十一岁，从十三四岁时，就已开始做汉人的向导，除了他的族兄马鲁外，很少有人能比他更熟悉这片大沙漠。"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"add","target":"char_wei_tian_peng","type":"主仆","intensity":30,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"苏玛是卫天鹏队伍的向导"}]}]}